  "detailed_description": "Cause chaos on an endless highway. Evade the police and survive as long as you can<br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> 64 Cars to unlock<br></li><li> Switch between cars by pressing space at any time<br></li><li> 3 Modes<br></li><li> Endless Destruction<br></li><li> High speed chases<br></li><li> Works on Steam Deck!</li></ul><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2264740/extras/32dda894bd2416bb1172cdfeebfcaa3b.poster.avif?t=1693390098\" width=480 height=480 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2264740/extras/32dda894bd2416bb1172cdfeebfcaa3b.webm?t=1693390098\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2264740/extras/32dda894bd2416bb1172cdfeebfcaa3b.mp4?t=1693390098\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Press space to slow time and select any highlighted car to switch to as often as you like.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2264740/extras/77df32167b4f1bf73d7408ac86960e9e.poster.avif?t=1693390098\" width=600 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2264740/extras/77df32167b4f1bf73d7408ac86960e9e.webm?t=1693390098\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2264740/extras/77df32167b4f1bf73d7408ac86960e9e.mp4?t=1693390098\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>The game takes place on an endless highway filled with traffic, allowing you to cause as much destruction as possible.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2264